creator: Big Ass Fans
descriptionHtml:
Use the i6 by BAF app to easily do the following:

- Select among your i6 fan’s seven unique speeds
- Adjust your LED light kit’s brightness and color temperature
- Customize your fan’s Auto settings to suit your comfort and lighting preferences
- Connect and control multiple i6 fans
- Link your fan with Nest or ecobee
- Learn how to connect your i6 fan to Amazon Alexa or The Google Assistant, for voice control and smart home integration
- Get help and find FAQs

Having trouble with an i6 device? Call 877-BIG-FANS to speak with a customer support specialist.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• i6 just got even smarter! A brand new scheduling feature makes your daily routine even easier!
• Just in time for summer, i6 now supports Whoosh Mode to mimic cooling natural breezes. Drink umbrellas not included.
• Added support for multiple i6 remote controls, up to three per fan.
• Now it’s even easier to link Alexa to your fan.
• Resolved issues on some newer Samsung mobile devices.
